Your Privacy

When you visit any website, it may store or retrieve information on your browser, mostly in the form of cookies. This information might be about you, your preferences or your device and is mostly used to make the site work as you expect it to. The information does not usually directly identify you, but it can give you a more personalized web experience. Because we respect your right to privacy, you can choose not to allow some types of cookies. Click on the different category headings to find out more and change our default settings. However, blocking some types of cookies may impact your experience of the site and the services we are able to offer.
More information

Strictly Necessary

Always Active

Our website won't work without these cookies. They are used for things like logging in, checking out and editing your details. These cookies are always on.

Functional Cookies

These cookies help us to make sure that your shopping experience is as good as it can be. You don't have to turn them on, but our website won't function as well for you.

Targeting / Advertising Cookies

Our advertising cookies reduce the number of adverts you see that might not be of interest to you. They mean that you are more likely to see your favourite Morrisons products advertised on our website, and other websites too.

Performance & Analytics Cookies

These cookies help us to understand which parts of our website customers enjoy and view most often. We use this information to make improvements to our website, and ensure our shopping experience is as good as it can be.
